# Resume task handoff (opt-in)

When the user invokes this rule (or uses the **`resume-task-handoff`** skill / phrase in **`docs/tasks/README.md`**):

1. Read **`docs/tasks/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md`**.
2. Follow links to **`docs/tasks/open/<slug>-handoff.md`** and the task **`docs/tasks/open/<slug>.md`**.
3. Continue from the **Next slice** / latest handoff section.

If **`CURRENT_HANDOFF.md`** is empty or indicates no active task, ask which open task to use or read **`docs/tasks/open/`** as appropriate.
